# Project: IsItBanned.com
- **Repo:** merlin-1776/isitbanned (GitHub)
- **Stack:** Astro 6 static site
- **Hosting:** Cloudflare Pages (project: isitbanned)
- **Domain:** isitbanned.com
- **Deploy:** npx astro build && npx wrangler pages deploy dist --project-name=isitbanned

## Buy Links & Fulfillment
- **Capital Books links:** point to store.capitalbooksonk.com/browse/filter/t/ISBN13/k/keyword
- **Bookshop.org:** affiliate ID 2537
- **Amazon:** affiliate tag sfbrweb-20

### Ingram Direct-to-Home Fulfillment (IN PROGRESS)
- **Goal:** Replace Capital Books webstore links with a checkout flow we control
- **Flow:** Customer buys → check Ingram stock → DTH order (ships to customer) → Capital Books keeps wholesale margin
- **Fallback:** If Ingram out of stock → route to Capital Books in-store inventory
- **Ingram account:** THERE & BACK AGAIN (#20AA780) — DTH enabled
- **Status:** Account on hold, Ross fixing. Once cleared:
  1. Test a DTH order manually via ipage browser
  2. Document shipping costs and pack slip branding
  3. Build automation (browser or API) to place orders
  4. Create checkout page (WooCommerce on capitalbooksonk.com or Stripe on isitbanned.com)
  5. Update all "Buy from Capital Books" links across 3,000+ book pages

## Roadmap
- [ ] **Phase 1:** Reach 3,000+ books in database (ongoing, PEN America data)
- [ ] **Phase 2:** Top 200 titles get "whyRead" editorial sections
- [ ] **Phase 3:** Ingram DTH fulfillment — turn buy links into real orders
- [ ] **Phase 4:** Expand DTH to all CBR sites (8 city book review sites)
- [ ] **Phase 5:** Expand DTH to Capital Books webstore (store.capitalbooksonk.com)
- [ ] **Phase 6:** Expand DTH to indie blog network (16 blogs)
